quadcast2srgb (0.2.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bugfix: rainbow display hue wrap-around now correct for negative rotation speeds.
  * Default config updated: static solid color replaced with a subtle color transition.

 -- Mario T <admin@muffinmar.io>  Wed, 28 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000

quadcast2srgb (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New display `transition`: cycling through n>=2 colors. 
    New CLI args: --transition-colors (comma-separated colors), --transition-speed, --transition-cubic-bezier. 
    New config args for `transition`: transition-colors, transition-speed, bezier.
  * New display `rainbow`: static or rolling rainbow across all LEDs.
    New CLI args: --rainbow-mode (flat|vertical|horizontal|diagonal), --rainbow-speed.
    New config args for `rainbow`: rainbow-mode, rainbow-speed.

 -- Mario T <admin@muffinmar.io>  Wed, 28 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000

